dhaar%20card%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Times%20of%20India.%20The%20police%20wrote%20to%20respective%20service%20providers%20ordering%20them%20to%20cancel%20the%20SIM%20cards%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIM%20cards%20were%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Polukonda%20Naveen%2C%20who%20distributes%20them%20to%20shops%20selling%20mobile%20phones%20and%20kiosks%20from%20where%20people%20can%20buy%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20rules%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecom%20(DoT)%2C%20a%20person%20is%20allowed%20to%20have%20nine%20SIM%20cards%20on%20one%20Aadhaar%20card.%20The%20facility%20is%20provided%20for%20large%20families%20where%20multiple%20connections%20can%20be%20taken%20by%20giving%20one%20Aadhaar%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20possibilities%20of%20this%20rule%20being%20misused.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20DoT%20has%20a%20website%20to%20check%20how%20many%20SIM%20cards%20are%20being%20used%20under%20your%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20logging%20on%20to%20tafcop.dgtelecom.gov.in%20(Sanchar%20Sathi)%2C%20a%20user%20can%20not%20only%20know%20the%20number%20of%20SIM%20cards%20issued%20under%20his%20name%20but%20also%20block%20the%20lost%20or%20stolen%20mobile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESteps%20to%20check%20how%20many%20SIM%20cards%20are%20issued%20on%20your%20Aadhaar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20logging%20on%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sancharsaathi.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3ESanchar%20Sathi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20user%20will%20see%20two%20links%20-%20block%20your%20lost%2Fstolen%20mobile%20and%20know%20your%20mobile%20connections%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EClicking%20on%20the%20second%20link%20will%20open%20a%20page%20where%20the%20user%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20enter%20the%2010-digit%20mobile%20number%2C%20captcha%20code%20and%20the%20OTP%20that%20will%20be%20received%20on%20the%20mobile%20number%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20page%20that%20