A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-ports-auditor-deloitte-plans-to-resign-after-flagging-concerns-123081100547_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-ports-auditor-deloitte-plans-to-resign-after-flagging-concerns-123081100547_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-ports-auditor-deloitte-plans-to-resign-after-flagging-concerns-123081100547_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Scared%2C%20Come%20Fast%5C%22%3A%20Jadavpur%20Student%20Told%20Mother%20Hour%20Before%20Fatal%20Fall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20who%20died%20after%20falling%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20a%20hostel%20in%20Kolkata's%20Jadavpur%20University%20had%20called%20his%20mother%20barely%20an%20hour%20before%20the%20incident%20and%20told%20her%20he%20was%20scared.%20He%20had%20pleaded%20with%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20a%20town%20100%20km%20away%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bcome%20fast%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20had%20lots%20to%20tell%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20and%20a%20classmate%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%2018-year-old%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20ragging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwapnadip%20Kundu%20was%20a%20first-year%20undergraduate%20student%20of%20Bengali%20(Honours)%20and%20had%20fallen%20from%20the%20balcony%20of%20the%20main%20hostel%20building%20in%20the%20university%20around%2011.45%20pm%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%204.30%20am%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSwapnadip%20spoke%20to%20his%20mother%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%20He%20told%20her%20he%20was%20not%20feeling%20good%20and%20was%20feeling%20scared.%20His%20mother%20asked%20him%20what%20had%20happened.%20He%20said%2C%20'You%20please%20come%20fast.%20I%20have%20lots%20of%20things%20to%20tell%20you'.%20Then%20she%20called%20him%20back%2C%20but%20the%20phone%20kept%20ringing%20and%20he%20did%20not%20pick%20up.%20About%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20his%20parents%20got%20a%20call%20asking%20them%20to%20go%20to%20Kolkata%20as%20their%20son%20had%20suffered%20a%20fall%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Swapnadip's%20uncle%2C%20Arup%20Kundu%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20body%20was%20completely%20covered%20but%20the%20doctor%20showed%20me%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20which%20indicated%20injury%20marks%20on%20his%20body.%20How%20does%20this%20happen%20if%20it%20was%20not%20ragging%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kundu%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwapnadip's%20father%2C%20Ramprasad%20Kundu.%20has%20complained%20to%20the%20police%20saying%20some%20of%20the%20boarders%20of%20the%20hostel%20are%20responsible%20for%20his%20son's%20death.%20A%20Facebook%20post%20by%20one%20of%20Swapnadip's%20classmates%2C%20Arpan%20Majhi%2C%20also%20pointed%20to%20ragging%20by%20%26quot%3Bsome%20seniors%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20had%20lost%20his%20classmate%20because%20of%20a%20few%20of%20them%2C%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20investigation%20and%20Jadavpur%20University%20has%20also%20remained%20tight-lipped.%20%C2%A0West%20Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20however%2C%20met%20the%20student's%20parents%20at%20the%20university%20campus%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20assured%20them%20of%20stern%20action%20against%20those%20responsible%20and%20said%20that%20the%20family%20would%20get%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20the%20Kundus'%20hometown%2C%20Bogula%20in%20Nadia%20district%2C%20held%20a%20protest%20today%2C%20demanding%20a%20proper%20investigation%20into%20Swapandip's%20death%20and%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20people%20responsible%20for%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20student%20Faizan%20Ahmed%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20his%20hostel%20room.%20While%20it%20was%20passed%20off%20as%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%2C%20the%20family%2C%20which%20is%20from%20Assam%2C%20had%20moved%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20claiming%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20ragging%20and%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20post-mortem%20was%20done%20this%20year%20after%20exhuming%20the%20body%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20high%20court.%20The%20autopsy%20report%20referred%20to%20injuries%20sustained%20before%20death%20and%20said%20they%20were%20homicidal%20in%20nature.%20His%20family%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20was%20pushed%20over%20the%20edge%20by%20ragging%20and%20that%20his%20complaints%20had%20gone%20unheard%20by%20IIT-Kharagpur's%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691754600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Ff8uuq8cs_jadavpur-university-fb_625x300_09_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscared-come-fast-jadavpur-student-told-mother-hour-before-fatal-fall-4290004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20student%20who%20died%20after%20falling%20from%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20a%20hostel%20in%20Kolkata's%20Jadavpur%20University%20had%20called%20his%20mother%20barely%20an%20hour%20before%20the%20incident%20and%20told%20her%20he%20was%20scared.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscared-come-fast-jadavpur-student-told-mother-hour-before-fatal-fall-4290004%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscared-come-fast-jadavpur-student-told-mother-hour-before-fatal-fall-4290004%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscared-come-fast-jadavpur-student-told-mother-hour-before-fatal-fall-4290004%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay's%20'OMG%202'%20has%20a%20fair%20start%20at%20BO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A16917545530