ridgeheads%20across%20the%20river%20as%20part%20of%20its%20counteroffensive.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20told%20Sky%20News%20that%20the%20raid%20appeared%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20distraction%20than%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20could%20encourage%20Russia%20to%20divert%20forces%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20attack%20and%20leave%20other%20parts%20of%20its%20defenses%20exposed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20breach%20they've%20made%20is%20south%20of%20Zaporizhzhia.%20They've%20got%20another%20one%20in%20Bakhmut%2C%20and%20another%20at%20Velyka%20Novosilka%20further%20south%20%E2%80%93%20so%20they've%20got%20at%20least%20four%20breaches%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20600-mile%20front%20line%20where%20Ukraine%20is%20seeking%20to%20punch%20through%20Russia's%20defensives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20going%20to%20try%20to%20go%20through%20one%20or%20more%20rather%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMick%20Ryan%2C%20a%20retired%20Australian%20Army%20major-general%20and%20military%20strategist%2C%20echoed%20that%20assessment%20in%20comments%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F9c031276-0990-4586-9c60-5f538eb16e4f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ukrainian%20armed%20forces%20will%20be%20hoping%20that%20the%20Kherson%20raid%20puts%20the%20Russians%20in%20a%20dilemma%20about%20whether%20Ukraine%20is%20going%20to%20do%20something%20more%20significant%20in%20Kherson%20or%E2%80%89.%E2%80%89.%E2%80%89.%E2%80%89draw%20off%20Russian%20reserves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20both%20sides%20were%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20find%20weaknesses%20in%20their%20adversary%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20luring%20them%20into%20diverting%20resources%20and%20spreading%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dnipro%20raid%20was%20mentioned%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20US%20think%20tank%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Institute%20for%20The%20Study%20of%20War%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20having%20initially%20been%20reported%20by%20Russian%20military%20bloggers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ISW%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bremains%20unclear%20whether%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20established%20an%20enduring%20presence%20on%20the%20east%20bank.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Ukraine%20established%20a%20bridgehead%20near%20the%20Antonovsky%20Bridge%20on%20the%20Dnipro%2C%20reports%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkyivindependent.com%2Fukrainian-troops-regularly-cross-dnipro-river-probing-russian-defenses-in-kherson-oblast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20Kyiv%20Independent%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Ukrainian%20military%20commander%20said%20that%20Ukrainian%20forces%20were%20conducting%20regular%20raids%20across%20the%20Dnipro%20to%20probe%20weaknesses%20in%20Russian%20defenses%2C%20and%20to%20distract%20Russian%20forces%20from%20shelling%20the%20nearby%20Ukrainian-held%20city%20of%20Kherson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20attack%20them%20where%20they%20least%20expect%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commander%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-daring-nighttime-raid-was-likely-a-distraction-experts-say-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691754537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d611717e9149001aa49ef1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-daring-nighttime-raid-was-likely-a-distraction-experts-say-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20seeking%20to%20breach%20Russia's%20formidable%20defenses%2C%20using%20full%20frontal%20attacks%20as%20well%20as%20feints%20to%20distract%20Russian%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-daring-nighttime-raid-was-likely-a-distraction-experts-say-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%222%20Minutes%20On%20Manipur%20In%202-Hour%20Speech%5C%22%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Targets%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStepping%20up%20the%20attack%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Friday%20said%20it%20does%20not%20behove%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20laugh%20and%20crack%20jokes%20in%20Parliament%20when%20the%20state%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bon%20fire%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20past%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20%26quot%3Bwants%20Manipur%20to%20burn%20and%20allows%20it%20to%20burn%26quot%3B%2C%20Gandhi%20alleged%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20AICC%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%20and%20asserted%20that%20if%20the%20Modi%20government%20wanted%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20there%20are%20tools%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20government%20that%20can%20stop%20it%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20and%20children%20are%20dying%20over%20there%2C%20women%20are%20being%20molested%20and%20raped%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Parliament%20and%20laughing.%20This%20is%20not%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20opposition%2C%20it%20is%20about%20India%2C%20it%20is%20about%20our%20country.%20A%20state%20has%20been%20decimated%2C%20it%20does%20not%20exist%20anymore%20and%20it%20has%20happened%20because%20of%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP%20--%20divide%20and%20rule%20and%20burn%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20strong%20attack%20came%20a%20day%20after%20PM%20Modi%20slammed%20the%20opposition%20in%20his%20over%20two-hour%20reply%20to%20the%20motion%20of%20no-confidence%20against%20his%20government%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20his%20remarks%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20%26quot%3Bmurdered%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur%26quot%3B%20were%20not%20hollow%20words%20as%20he%20had%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%2019%20years%20in%20politics%20been%20told%20in%20a%20state%20that%20if%20he%20takes%20a%20person%20from%20one%20community%20in%20his%20security%20detail%20to%20the%20area%20of%20another%20community%2C%20they%20will%20shoot%20that%20security%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20watched%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20yesterday%2C%20speaking%20for%20two%20hours%2C%20laughing%2C%20joking%2C%20and%20raising%20slogans%20in%20Parliament.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20would%20say%20one%20line%20and%20the%20BJP%20(leaders)%20would%20shout%20another%20slogan.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20seems%20to%20have%20forgotten%20that%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20is%20on%20fire%20and%20has%20been%20on%20fire%20for%20four%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20does%20not%20behove%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20that%20when%20there%20is%20violence%20in%20the%20country%2C%20he%20indulges%20in%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20fun%20for%20two%20hours%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20went%20to%20Manipur%20and%20went%20to%20the%20Meitei%20area%20we%20were%20told%20that%20they%20want%20us%20to%20come%2C%20they%20love%20us%2C%20but%20we%20should%20not%20have%20any%20Kuki%20in%20our%20security%20detail%20or%20they%20will%20be%20shot.%20We%20were%20told%20the%20same%20thing%20when%20we%20were%20going%20to%20the%20Kuki%20area%20about%20Meitei%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20central%20security%20personnel%20told%20him%20in%20Manipur%20that%20they%20had%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20I%20said%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20has%20been%20murdered%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Manipur.%20I%20was%20not%20speaking%20metaphorically%2C%20I%20was%20speaking%20literally%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Congress%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20in%20my%20speech%20(in%20Lok%20Sabha)%20I%20said%20Bharat%20Mata%20has%20been%20murdered%20in%20Manipur.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20words%20Bharat%20Mata%20have%20been%20expunged%20from%20Parliament.%20It%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20those%20words.%20What%20is%20it%20that%20I%20have%20said%20is%20wrong%3F%20I%20have%20said%20Bharat%20Mata%2C%20which%20is%20the%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20where%20everybody%20lives%20peacefully%2C%20harmoniously%20and%20with%20affection%2C%20has%20been%20killed%20in%20Manipur%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fact%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20no%20longer%20exists%20as%20a%20state%20because%20the%20state%20requires%20control%20and%20authority%20which%20have%20disappeared%20from%20there%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20take%20the%20Indian%20Army%20two%20days%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bnonsense%26quot%3B%20going%20on%20there%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20refuses%20to%20stop%20the%20fire%2C%20he%20wants%20Manipur%20to%20burn%2C%20he%20allows%20Manipur%20to%20burn%20because%20if%20he%20did%20want%20it%20to%20stop%2C%20there%20are%20tools%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20government%20that%20can%20stop%20it%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20Indian%20army%2C%20every%20Indian%20knows%20that%20if%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20told%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20(violence)%2C%20it%20will%20stop%20immediately.%20There%20are%20reasons%20for%20the%20PM%20not%20being%20able%20to%20go%20to%20Manipur.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20speak%20about%20them%20publicly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20%26quot%3Bridiculed%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20and%20the%20women%20there%20in%20his%20address%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20asserted%20that%20when%20a%20person%20becomes%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20ceases%20to%20be%20a%20politician%20and%20should%20become%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20politics%20should%20be%20put%20aside%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20should%20not%20speak%20as%20a%20petty%20politician%2C%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20political%20party%2C%20but%20he%20should%20speak%20with%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%20behind%20him.%20It%20is%20tragic%20to%20watch%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20it%20is%20sad%20because%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20does%20not%20understand%20what%20he%20actually%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20our%20representative%2C%20he%20is%20my%20representative%20and%20watching%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20spend%20two%20hours%20talking%20about%20the%20Congress%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20opposition%2C%20making%20ridiculous%20remarks%20about%20the%20name%20(of%20the%20opposition%20alliance)%2C%20this%20really%20does%20not%20do%20justice%20to%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20prime%20ministers%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP.%20I%20have%20seen%20Mr%20(Atal%20Bihari)%20Vajpayee%2C%20and%20I%20have%20seen%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda.%20There%20is%20a%20complete%20misunderstanding%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20about%20what%20the%20PM%20of%20India%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20reitera