22Autonomy%5C%22%20Under%20Elon%20Musk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELinda%20Yaccarino%2C%20the%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20has%20stated%20that%20she%20has%20the%20%26quot%3Bautonomy%26quot%3B%20to%20run%20the%20company%20under%20Elon%20Musk.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F08%2F10%2Fx-corp-ceo-linda-yaccarino-says-she-has-autonomy-under-elon-musk.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20added%20that%20their%20%26quot%3Broles%20are%20very%20clear%26quot%3B%20and%20advertisers%20should%20be%20comfortable%20to%20return%20to%20the%20social%20media%20platform.%20%26quot%3BElon%20is%20working%20on%20accelerating%20the%20rebrand%20and%20working%20on%20the%20future.%20And%20I'm%20responsible%20for%20the%20rest.%20Running%20the%20company%2C%20from%20partnerships%20to%20legal%20to%20sales%20to%20finance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Yaccarino%20asserted%20that%20X%20is%20focused%20on%20turning%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20app%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20include%20payment%20processing%20and%20video%20calls%20without%20the%20need%20for%20a%20phone%20number.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20she%20provided%20a%20timeline%20of%20%26quot%3Bexperiences%20and%20evolution%26quot%3B%20initiated%20by%20the%20platform%20under%20Mr%20Musk's%20leadership.%20She%20cited%20examples%20of%20long-form%20video%2C%20articles%2C%20subscriptions%20and%20creator%20earnings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20company's%20decision%20to%20let%20go%20off%20Twitter%20branding%20completely.%20%26quot%3BElon%20has%20been%20talking%20about%20X%2C%20the%20everything%20app%2C%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Yaccarino%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%20%26quot%3BEven%20when%20we%20announced%20that%20I%20was%20joining%20the%20company%2C%20I%20was%20joining%20the%20company%20to%20partner%20with%20Elon%20to%20transform%20Twitter%20into%20X%2C%20the%20everything%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20believes%20that%20rebranding%20to%20X%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bliberation%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20previous%20name.%20%26quot%3BA%20liberation%20that%20allowed%20us%20to%20evolve%20past%20a%20legacy%20mindset%20and%20thinking.%20And%20to%20reimagine%20how%20everyone%2C%20how%20everyone%20on%20Spaces%20who's%20listening%2C%20everybody%20who's%20watching%20around%20the%20world.%20It's%20going%20to%20change%20how%20we%20congregate%2C%20how%20we%20entertain%2C%20how%20we%20transact%20all%20in%20one%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Yaccarino%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20stay%20Twitter%2C%20or%20you%20stay%20whatever%20your%20previous%20brand%20is%2C%20change%20tends%20to%20be%20only%20incremental.%20And%20you%20get%20graded%20by%20a%20legacy%20report%20card.%20And%20at%20X%20we%20think%20about%20what's%20possible.%20Not%20the%20incremental%20change%20of%20what%20can't%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELinda%20Yaccarino%20was%20a%20former%20NBCUniversal%20executive%2C%20who%20formally%20joined%20as%20the%20company's%20CEO%20in%20June.%20She%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20she%20has%20been%20inspired%20by%20owner%20Elon%20Musk's%20vision%20to%20create%20a%20brighter%20future%20and%20is%20excited%20to%20help%20to%20transform%20the%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691753580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F5k7toag_linda-yaccarino-linkedin_625x300_12_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froles-are-clear-linda-yaccarino-says-she-has-autonomy-to-run-x-under-elon-musk-4289926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CEO%20believes%20that%20rebranding%20to%20X%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bliberation%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20previous%20name.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2