20commander-in-chief.%20In%202008%2C%20fuelled%20by%20a%20brilliantly%20innovative%2C%20multi-pronged%20social%20media%20campaign%2C%20Barack%20Hussein%20Obama%20became%20the%20first%20black%20President%20of%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20rousing%20rallying%20cry%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20can!%E2%80%9D%20ricocheted%20around%20the%20internet%20along%20with%20his%20hope-filled%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20begin%20the%20next%20great%20chapter%20in%20the%20American%20story%20with%20three%20words%20that%20will%20ring%20from%20coast%20to%20coast%2C%20from%20sea%20to%20shining%20sea.%E2%80%9D%20Social%20media%20had%20indubitably%20helped%20push%20back%20the%20racist%20bigots%2C%20but%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20only%20fleetingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20who%20can%20forget%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2011%2Ffeb%2F25%2Ftwitter-facebook-uprisings-arab-libya%5C%22%3Eseminal%20role%20played%20by%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20revolutionary%20movements%20for%20democracy%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20between%202010%20and%202012%3F%20Social%20media%20helped%20protesters%20to%20mobilise%20support%2C%20shape%20opinions%2C%20organise%20mass%20demonstrations%20and%20inform%20the%20world%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20autocracies%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dramatic%20reversal%20of%20roles%2C%20state%20propaganda%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20a%20social%20media%20blitzkrieg%20that%20amplified%20the%20dissenting%20voices%20of%20the%20common%20citizens.%20Social%20media%20had%20struck%20a%20decisive%20blow%20for%20democracy%20by%20helping%20unseat%20an%20unsavoury%20gang%20of%20autocrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1024px-2011_Egyptian_protests_Facebook__jan25_card.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-153149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protester%20holding%20a%20placard%20in%20Cairo%20referring%20to%20Facebook%2C%20acknowledging%20social%20media%E2%80%99s%20role%20during%20the%202011%20Egyptian%20Revolution.%20Photo%3A%20Essam%20Sharaf%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%20Unported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20laudable%20exemplars%20of%20the%20potential%20of%20social%20media%20to%20democratise%20global%20discourse%20and%20promote%20the%20common%20good%20proved%20deceptive.%20In%20the%20fractious%20arena%20of%20power%20politics%2C%20social%20media%20has%20become%20the%20prime%20means%20of%20communication%2C%20but%20that%20weighty%20responsibility%20has%20not%20been%20complemented%20by%20responsible%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20tech%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20putative%20gatekeepers%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20cussedly%20reluctant%20to%20flag%20and%20remove%20inappropriate%2C%20offensive%20matter%2C%20largely%20because%20hate%20speech%20and%20incitement%20to%20violence%20is%20lucrative%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPracticing%20an%20unrestrained%20free%20speech%20absolutism%20where%20the%20hitherto%20unsayable%20is%20now%20par%20for%20the%20course%2C%20social%20media%20is%20dominated%20by%20a%20bewildering%20mix%20of%20right-wing%20nationalists%2C%20hatemongers%2C%20Islamophobic%20edgelords%20and%20Twitterati%20warriors%20who%20have%20corroded%20the%20entire%20system%20with%20the%20most%20unspeakable%2C%20venomous%20and%20divisive%20rhetoric%2C%20creating%20a%20dystopian%20world%20where%20there%20are%20no%20moral%20codes%20and%20where%20every%20fact%20is%20negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20platforms%2C%20largely%20unmoderated%2C%20have%20become%20cesspools%20of%20toxic%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20frightening%20that%20social%20media%20has%20become%2C%20for%20most%20users%2C%20the%20sole%20fount%20of%20information%20and%20knowledge%20about%20the%20world%20around%20them.%20It%20gives%20them%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20power%20to%20avenge%20wrongs%20and%20punish%20enemies%2C%20while%20also%20providing%20them%20an%20outlet%20to%20vent%20their%20fears%20and%20insecurities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20lethal%20arsenal%20of%20disinformation%2C%20alternative%20facts%2C%20violent%20trolling%2C%20doctored%20videos%2C%20odious%20propaganda%20%3Cem%3Eet%20al%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20social%20media%20has%20seized%20absolute%20control%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinformation%20war%E2%80%9D%2C%20even%20as%20the%20traditional%20media%20outlets%20shrink%20rapidly.%20The%20measured%2C%20thought-provoking%20op-eds%20have%20been%20supplanted%20by%20intellectually%20undemanding%20social%20media%20fare%2C%20a%20dumbing%20down%20that%20bodes%20ill%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-its-media-information-that-keeps-india-as-a-country-together-or-apart%5C%22%3EBackstory%3A%20It%E2%80%99s%20Media%20Information%20That%20Keeps%20India%20as%20a%20Country%20Together%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Apart%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20accident%20that%20the%20weaponising%20of%20social%20media%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20two%20largest%20democracies%20coincided%20with%20the%20rise%20to%20power%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20two%20leaders%20whose%20careers%20have%20been%20greatly%20influenced%2C%20if%20not%20defined%2C%20by%20their%20deep-rooted%2C%20visceral%20links%20with%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20universally%20recognised%20as%20the%20leading%20troll%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20July%202019%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202020%20presidential%20elections%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fwhite-house%2Ftrump-touts-power-controversial-social-media-activists-white-house-summit-n1029036%5C%22%3Ehe%20convened%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20media%20summit%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inviting%20a%20gaggle%20of%20pro-Trump%20social%20media%20titans%20to%20strategise%20for%20the%20ensuing%20presidential%20elections.%20Social%20media%20constituted%20the%20main%20plank%20of%20his%20election%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20renowned%20for%20his%20fidelity%20to%20the%20truth%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20the%20role%20of%20social%20media%20is%20a%20stunning%20example%20of%20two-facedness.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpmoindia%2Fstatus%2F647974165140533248%5C%22%3Estated%20position%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20media%20is%20reducing%20social%20barriers.%20It%20connects%20people%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20human%20values%2C%20not%20identities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20ugly%20reality%20is%20that%20he%20is%20a%20committed%20Hindu%20supremacist%2C%20whose%20camp%20followers%20have%20been%20persecuting%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20amid%20electorally-inspired%20outreach%20targeting%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20and%20a%20section%20of%20compromised%20Christian%20clergy%20%E2%80%93%20duplicitous%20gestures%20that%20fool%20nobody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20book%20%3Cem%3EI%20am%20a%20Troll%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20intrepid%20journalist%20Swati%20Chaturvedi%20takes%20us%20into%20the%20dark%20recesses%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20world%2C%20whose%20main%20purpose%20is%20to%20purvey%20fake%20news%2C%20foment%20hatred%2C%20pillory%20opponents%2C%20empower%20bigotry%2C%20incite%20violence%20and%20undermine%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20the%20target%20of%20the%20most%20scurrilous%20attacks%20by%20right-wing%20trolls%20and%20facing%20sustained%20harassment%20by%20the%20government%2C%20she%20stood%20her%20ground.%20She%20holds%20the%20PM%20responsible%20for%20emboldening%20them%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20watching%20in%20horrified%20fascination%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20follows%20and%20felicitates%20trolls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-twitter-trolls-free-expression%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20His%20Troll%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20an%20age%20of%20viral%20politics%2C%20where%20grassroots%20support%20is%20driven%20primarily%20by%20the%20internet%2C%20which%20is%20setting%20the%20agenda%20because%20of%20its%20omnipresence%20and%20unfiltered%20instant%20feedback.%20The%20days%20when%20voters%20took%20their%20cues%20from%20the%20studied%20analyses%20of%20the%20political%20pundits%20are%20over%2C%20as%20the%20vast%20majority%20turn%20to%20social%20media%20for%20determining%20their%20world%20view%20and%20certainly%20their%20electoral%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20I.N.D.I.A%20had%20better%20watch%20out!%20The%202024%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20fought%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20social%20media%2C%20which%20now%20occupies%20a%20central%20place%20in%20our%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20will%20not%20be%20a%20level%20playing%20field!%20As%20we%20head%20into%20the%20final%20lap%20of%20the%20election%20cycle%2C%20this%20dispensation%E2%80%99s%20troll%20armies%20will%20be%20going%20full%20tilt%20with%20their%20repertoire%20of%20dirty%20tricks%20%E2%80%93%20fake%20news%2C%20doctored%20videos%2C%20bigotry%2C%20polarising%20hate%2C%20incitement%20to%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20have%20a%20free%20run%2C%20the%20surveillance%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20curbs%20on%20the%20free%20speech%20of%20opponents%20and%20critics%20of%20the%20regime%20will%20be%20intensified.%20It%20is%20a%20formidable%20challenge%2C%20but%20how%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20people%20who%20care%20for%20democracy%20respond%20to%20the%20machinations%20of%20this%20dangerous%20outfit%20will%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20our%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20hr