nitoring%20of%2066%20sampled%20projects%20being%20implemented%20under%20Phase-I%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20revealed%20instances%20of%20irregularities%20in%20the%20allocation%20of%20projects%20by%20implementing%20agencies%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20tendering%20protocols.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20successful%20bidder%20did%20not%20fulfill%20the%20tendering%20condition%20or%20the%20bidder%20was%20selected%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20falsified%20documents.%20Works%20were%20awarded%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20detailed%20project%20reports%2C%20or%20there%20were%20faulty%20project%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcag-flags-bharatmala-bidding-irregularities%2Farticleshow%2F102625792.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20implementing%20agencies%20were%20awarding%20projects%20without%20ensuring%20availability%20of%20required%20land%20and%20forest%20clearance%2C%20which%20are%20resulting%20in%20delayed%20commencement%20and%20completion%20of%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20and%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20are%20the%20implementing%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20also%20found%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20appraisal%20and%20approval%20mechanism%20proposed%20to%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20in%20many%20of%20the%20high%20cost%20Engineering%20Procurement%20and%20Construction%20(EPC)%20projects%20or%20fully%20funded%20government%20projects.%20The%20Delhi-Vadodara%20Expressway%20and%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20could%20not%20be%20assessed%20either%20by%20the%20CCEA%20or%20the%20highways%20ministry%20to%20be%20scrutinised%20at%20that%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20appraisal%20and%20approval%20mechanism%20decided%20by%20CCEA%20was%20also%20not%20strictly%20followed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CAG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20were%20significant%20cost%20overruns.%20It%20noted%20that%20only%2075.62%25%20of%20CCEA%20approved%20length%20has%20been%20awarded%20while%20158.24%25%20of%20approved%20financial%20outlay%20was%20sanctioned%20up%20to%20March%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Phase-I%20of%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%20was%20for%20development%20up%20to%20September%202022%2C%20at%20an%20investment%20outlay%20of%20Rs%205%2C35%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Finfrastructure%2Fcag-flags-irregularities-in-bharatmala-project-tenders%2Farticleshow%2F102617116.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20the%20CAG%20report%2C%20that%20significant%20changes%20made%20in%20the%20scope%20of%20projects%20and%20cost%20estimates%20as%20well%20as%20richer%20project%20specifications%20adopted%20have%20pushed%20up%20the%20sanctioned%20cost%20of%20projects.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20resulted%20in%20sanctioned%20civil%20cost%20being%20Rs%2023.89%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20(km)%20as%20against%20the%20CCEA%20approved%20cost%20of%20Rs%2013.98%20crore%20per%20km%20and%20sanctioned%20pre-construction%20cost%20being%20Rs%208.28%20crore%20per%20km%20as%20against%20the%20CCEA%20approved%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.39%20crore%20per%20km%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20auditor%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20report%2C%20the%20CAG%20found%20that%20NHAI%20continued%20to%20collect%20user%20fee%20in%20three%20toll%20plazas%20(namely%20Nathavalasa%2C%20Chalageri%2C%20Hebbalu%20in%20Southern%20India)%20during%20delayed%20period%20of%20construction.%20This%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20rules%20stating%20that%20no%20user%20fee%20shall%20be%20levied%20for%20the%20delayed%20period%2C%20leading%20to%20higher%20toll%20collection%20from%20commuters%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691752840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F25192431%2FA-man-crosses-empty-NH24-whichnis-otherwisr-heavy-in-traffic-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-finds-irregularities-in-award-of-highway-projects-under-bharatmala-pariyojana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CAG%20report%20found%20irregularities%20by%20implementing%20agencies%20in%20project%20allocation%2C%20violating%20tendering%20rules.%20This%20included%20cases%20where%20winning%20bidders%20didn't%20meet%20conditions%2C%20were%20chosen%20with%20fake%20documents%2C%20and%20projects%20were%20awarded%20without%20proper%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-finds-irregularities-in-award-of-highway-projects-under-bharatmala-pariyojana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20change%20your%20Facebook%20password%20to%20keep%20your%20account%20safe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222166%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22using%20laptop%20at%20home%20typing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60b68b82bee0fc0019d5ab46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20several%20ways%20to%20change%20your%20Facebook%20password%20and%20enhance%20your%20security.%3Cp%3ELuis%20Alvarez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20should%20change%20your%20Facebook%20password%20regularly%20to%20keep%20your%20account%20and%20data%20secure.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20change%20your%20Facebook%20password%2C%20go%20to%20the%20Meta%20Account%20Center.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20haven't%20already%2C%20you%20should%20also%20enable%20tw