ar%20over%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Germany's%20recent%20drop%20in%20inflation%2C%20food%20prices%20still%20remain%2011%25%20higher%20this%20month%20compared%20to%2012%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20temporarily%20hiked%20some%20prices%20to%20comment%20on%20how%20food%20prices%20are%20not%20fully%20indicative%20of%20broader%20long-term%20environmental%20and%20health%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20customers%20applauded%20the%20idea%2C%20while%20others%20deemed%20it%20a%20stunt%20directed%20at%20consumers%20and%20not%20the%20unsustainable%20agriculture%20practices%20themselves.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurotopics.net%2Fen%2F305415%2Freal-prices-at-penny-pr-stunt-or-the-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20Austrian%20paper%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bfood%20prices%20are%20far%20too%20low%26quot%3B%20and%20noted%20that%20demanding%20higher%20prices%20to%20account%20for%20environmental%20costs%20%26quot%3Bonly%20puts%20more%20financial%20strain%20on%20end%20consumers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20already%20struggling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20many%20of%20our%20customers%20are%20suffering%20from%20today's%20unrelentingly%20high%20food%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Stefan%20Go%CC%88rgens%2C%20the%20COO%20at%20Penny%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BStill%2C%20we%20have%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20one%20unpleasant%20fact%20of%20life%3A%20Our%20food%20prices%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20consequential%20environmental%20costs%20that%20arise%20along%20our%20supply%20chain.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20experiment%2C%20the%20Nuremberg%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Greifswald%20will%20analyze%20the%20data%20and%20develop%20recommended%20courses%20of%20action%2C%20such%20as%20creating%20policies%20that%20will%20guide%20the%20country%20to%20a%20more%20sustainable%20future.%20The%20additiona