%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20veiled%20dig%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20his%20absence%20from%20parliament%20on%20the%20first%20two%20days%20of%20the%20debate.%20%26quot%3BThe%20House%20is%20in%20session%20and%20people%20remain%20busy%20roaming%20around%20(ghoomte%20rahte%20hain).%20When%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20used%20to%20be%20in%20power%20and%20I%20was%20one%20of%20his%20ministers.%20We%20used%20to%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20remain%20inside%20the%20House%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20inquire%20with%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%2C%20they%20will%20agree%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20only%20focused%20on%20campaigns%20and%20publicity.%20Can%20you%20see%20any%20development%20initiatives%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20snapped%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20last%20year.%20He%20later%20took%20oath%20as%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20the%20eighth%20after%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)-RJD%20government%20completed%20one%20year%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20remarks%20come%20a%20day%20after%20Bihar%20BJP%20president%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%20launched%20a%20blistering%20attack%20on%20the%20'Mahagathbandhan'%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20%26quot%3Bcrutch%20politics%26quot%3B%20was%20coming%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20become%20a%20symbol%20of%20bad%20governance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691747340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fvd95hai_nitish-kumar-pti_625x300_29_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-bjp-jdu-bjp-will-be-wiped-out-from-bihar-in-2024-nitish-kumars-big-prediction-4289369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20predicted%20a%20wipeout%20for%20the%20BJP