s%20international%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Bhatt%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20promising%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20has%20to%20suffer%20from%20in%20this%20Tom%20Harper%20film%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20indignity.%20Playing%20the%20role%20of%20a%2022-year-old%20whizkid%20hacker%20named%20Keya%20Dhawan%2C%20Bhatt%20is%20mostly%20required%20to%20flash%20her%20luminous%20smile%20after%20delivering%20a%20snappy%20one-liner.%20And%20then%20feign%20surprise%20during%20the%20most%20basic%20plot-points%20of%20the%20film.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20told%20me%20you%20wanted%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20Charter%2C%20not%20kill%20the%20people%20running%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shrieks%20at%20someone.%20Bhatt%2C%20who%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20of%20Bollywood%20by%20subverting%20ing%C3%A9nue%20parts%20with%20her%20spunk%2C%20is%20tasked%20with%20playing%20the%20outline%20of%20an%20ing%C3%A9nue%20here.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20sincere%20through%20most%20of%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20film%20that%20is%20the%20bigger%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20follows%20a%20secret%20spy%20outfit%20called%20the%20Charter%20%E2%80%93%20a%20body%20of%20international%20spies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20operates%20from%20the%20shadows.%20When%20international%20incidents%20get%20out%20of%20hand%2C%20the%20Charter%20intervenes.%20They%E2%80%99re%20guided%20by%20some%20supercomputer%20called%20the%20Heart%2C%20which%20can%20hack%20into%20any%20system%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world%20thereby%20giving%20it%20absolute%20power%20in%20an%20increasingly%20digital%20world.%20It%20sounds%20eerily%20similar%20to%20the%20plot%20of%20%3Cem%3EMission%20Impossible%3A%20Dead%20Reckoning%20%E2%80%93%20Part%20One%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20Cruise%20and%20his%20colleagues%20chase%20a%20programme%20called%20The%20Entity.%20The%20only%20difference%20here%20is%20that%20the%20Heart%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20sentient%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERachel%20Stone%20(Gal%20Gadot)%20is%20a%20devoted%20member%20of%20the%20Charter%2C%20with%20a%20vague%20and%20generic%20past.%20She%20pulls%20off%20daredevil%20stunts%2C%20has%20the%20odd%20sentimental%20moment%20of%20reflection%2C%20but%20a%20big%20part%20of%20her%20job%20is%20to%20get%20on%20the%20radio%20only%20to%20say%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20fine%E2%80%9D%20after%20escaping%20near-certain%20death%20yet%20again.%20There%E2%80%99s%20little%20doubt%20about%20Gadot%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20as%20an%20action%20star%20%E2%80%93%20but%20after%20%3Cem%3EWonder%20Woman%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2017)%2C%20each%20successive%20project%20of%20hers%20has%20chipped%20away%20at%20her%20credibility%20as%20even%20a%20barebones%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM-300x229.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11143259%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.31.00-PM-1024x783.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGal%20Gadot%20in%20Heart%20of%20Stone%20(2023).%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20issues%20with%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20how%20little%20of%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20voice%20of%20its%20own.%20The%20Charter%20seems%20to%20be%20borrowing%20from%20the%20age-old%20trope%20of%20secret%20societies%20of%20assassins%2Fspies%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20was%20recently%20rehashed%20in%20the%20Amazon%20original%2C%20Citadel.%20A%20machine%20dictating%20missions%2C%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20highly-trained%20spies%20simply%20take%20its%20word%20without%20exercising%20their%20own%20discretion%2C%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20everything%20from%20Minority%20Report%20(2002)%20to%20Wanted%20(2008).%20The%20plot%20line%20of%20a%20former%20spy%20abandoned%20by%20his%20agency%2C%20coming%20back%20to%20get%20his%20revenge%2C%20is%20a%20trope%20that%20has%20been%20around%20forever%2C%20most%20prominently%20in%20Skyfall%20(2012).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomehow%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20considered%20acceptable%20that%20one%20organisation%20wields%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Heart%2C%20and%20thereby%20make%20the%20calls%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98greater%20good%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20even%20Tom%20Cruise%20struggles%20with%20in%20the%20latest%20Mission%20Impossible%20film.%20Therefore%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20villains%20in%20this%20film%20(ably%20supported%20by%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20baby-faced%20hacker)%20will%20try%20and%20steal%20the%20Heart.%20Gadot%20must%20stop%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20a%20plot%20as%20superficial%20as%20this%20though%2C%20there%20might%20still%20be%20room%20for%20fun.%20A%20few%20imaginative%20action%20set-pieces%2C%20some%20unexpected%20humour%2C%20at%20least%20some%20personality%20to%20the%20characters%20beyond%20their%20cursory%20outline.%20Alas%2C%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20Netflix%20assembly-line%20of%20action%20films%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20which%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20same%20bluish%20tinge%2C%20the%20action%20choreography%20seems%20to%20mistake%20loudness%20for%20scale%2C%20and%20the%20one-liners%20seem%20to%20have%20the%20smugness%20of%20a%20Marvel%20superhero%20film.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20harsh%20to%20say%20that%20Heart%20of%20Stone%20feels%20like%20a%20microwaved%20version%20of%20all%20leftover%20tropes%20from%20action%20films%20from%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20film%20that%20is%20hinged%20on%20a%20futuristic%20technology%20like%20an%20AI%2C%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20of%20Stone%3C%2Fem%3E%20feels%20weirdly%20dated.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20frantic%20%E2%80%98hacking%20scenes%E2%80%99%20seem%20reminiscent%20of%20giddy%20%E2%80%9890s%20action%20films%20that%20usually%20employed%20a%20%E2%80%98hacker%E2%80%99%20to%20conjure%20all%20the%20contrivances%20a%20screenwriter%20could%20think%20of.%20Solid%20actors%20like%20Sophie%20Okonedo%20and%20Jamie%20Dornan%20are%20wasted%20in%20roles%20needing%20them%20to%20rally%20around%20Gadot%20%E2%80%93%20so%20that%20she%20can%20have%20her%20own%20action%20franchise%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20unintentionally%20funny%20thing%20about%20Harper%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20that%20a%20billion-dollar%20corporation%20leads%20with%20knowing%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20potential%2C%20and%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20confidently%20waste%20her%20talents.%20They%E2%80%99re%20clueless%2C%20just%20like%20in%20the%20matters%20of%20the%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691746240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11144042%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-2.27.23-PM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fheart-of-stone-alia-bhatts-lifeless-hollywood-debut-in-a-tired-cliched-spy-movie%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Netflix%20formula%20for%20action%20films%20is%20resolutely%20stuck%20in%20the%20past%2C%20churning%20out%20the%20same%20old%20set%20pieces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fheart-of-stone-alia-bhatts-lifeless-hollywood-debut-in-a-tired-cliched-spy-movie%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sarajevo%20Film%20Festival%20Commemorat