omens-event-12937802%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20company%20runs%20on%20a%204-day%20workweek.%20Our%20days%20can%20be%20intense%20but%20revenue%20has%20increased%20and%20we're%20never%20going%20back.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Rosenbauer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d53ee77e9149001aa446f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20Rosenbauer%20is%20a%2031-year-old%20founder%20and%20CEO.%20%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rosenbauer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETaylor%20Rosenbauer%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20RocketAir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20company%20switched%20to%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20and%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20revenue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERosenbauer%20says%20that%20a%20shortened%20work%20week%20is%20more%20intense%20but%20employees%20love%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Taylor%20Rosenbauer%2C%20the%2031-year-old%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20global%20design%20and%20strategy%20firm%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketair.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ERocketAir%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20company%20adopted%20a%20permanent%20four-day%20workweek%20in%20November%202022%20and%20I%20believe%20our%20employees%20love%20it%2C%20our%20clients%20love%20it%2C%20and%20we're%20never%20going%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERocketAir%20%E2%80%94%20a%20global%20design%20and%20strategy%20firm%20with%2022%20full-time%20team%20members%20%E2%80%94%20has%20worked%20remotely%20since%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20been%20in%20business%20for%20four%20years%20when%20the%20idea%20for%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20came%20up.%20I'd%20heard%20about%20companies%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20experimenting%20with%20a%20four-day%20workweek%2C%20and%20it%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20cautious%20that%20it%20might%20not%20work%20for%20a%20company%20like%20us%20that's%20in%20the%20client%20services%20business%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20there%20was%20a%20chance%20we%20could%20make%20it%20work%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20that%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFitting%20five%20days'%20worth%20of%20work%20into%20four%20days%20wasn't%20a%20smooth%20transition%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20expect%20it%20to%20be%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20is%20so%20entrenched%20in%20society.%20That's%20why%20we%20started%20with%20a%20three-month%20trial%20period.%20At%20the%20beginning%20of%20our%20pilot%2C%20we%20were%20honest%20that%20it%20might%20not%20stick%3B%20fortunately%2C%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20approach%20included%20multiple%20pulse%20surveys%20to%20see%20how%20it%20was%20working%20for%20every%20member%20of%20the%20team.%20The%20survey%20asked%20team%20members%20to%20rate%20how%20they%20were%20feeling%20about%20progress%20in%20tasks%2C%20projects%2C%20and%20goals%3B%20people%2C%20interactions%2C%20and%20team%20dynamics%3B%20work-life%20balance%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20general%20wellness%3B%20and%20learning%2C%20development%2C%20and%20feedback.%20We%20also%20included%20an%20optional%20opportunity%20to%20share%20anything%20else%20that%20was%20on%20their%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20showed%20increased%20employee%20well-being%2C%20productivity%2C%20and%20work%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20conducted%20pulse%20surveys%20every%20month%20during%20the%20pilot%20and%20found%20that%20for%20our%20employees%20with%20young%20children%20at%20home%2C%20the%20four-day%20workweek%20has%20been%20a%20game%20changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20feedback%20included%20improved%20mental%20health%2C%20more%20time%20to%20address%20personal%20development%20outside%20of%20work%2C%20and%20looking%20forward%20to%20work%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20condensed%20workweek%20can%20be%20more%20intense%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20heard%20from%20employees%20that%20they%20loved%20the%20four-day%20workweek%20and%20never%20wanted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20old%20way.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20were%20finding%20their%20work%20days%20more%20jam-packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20enacted%20the%20shorter%20workweek%2C%20we%20didn't%20mandate%20extended%20workdays.%20But%20because%20we%20have%20a%20responsibility%20to%20our%20clients%20to%20continue%20our%20same%20level%20of%20productivity%20and%20condense%20it%20into%20a%20shorter%20week%2C%20we%20sometimes%20need%20to%20work%20longer%20than%20a%20standard%209-to-5%20workday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20mitigate%20this%2C%20we%20advise%20that%20no%20meetings%20are%20scheduled%20after%205%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20team%20members%20block%20off%20their%20calendars%20for%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20things%20done%2C%20and%20they%20choose%20their%20communication%20method%20thoughtfully%20%E2%80%94%20does%20this%20need%20to%20be%20a%20meeting%20or%20could%20it%20be%20a%20Slack%20message%2C%20email%2C%20or%20Loom%20video%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollaborating%20with%20other%20teams%20that%20expect%20to%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20on%20Fridays%20was%20an%20expected%20hurdle.%20We%20knew%20that%20communicating%20and%20holding%20boundaries%20would%20be%20a%20critical%20aspect%20of%20the%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20credit%20goes%20to%20our%20communication%20strategy%20for%20making%20these%20conversations%20simple%20and%20straightforward.%20Prior%20to%20the%20four-day%20workweek%2C%20we%20had%20implemented%20a%20%26quot%3BNo%20Meeting%20Fridays%26quot%3B%20policy%2C%20which%20was%20a%20nice%20interim%20step%20that%20helped%20our%20team%20develop%20the%20habit%20of%20protecting%20their%20time%20and%20communicating%20that%20to%20external%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20shorter%20workweek%20encourages%20everyone%20to%20work%20more%20efficiently%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20challenged%20us%20to%20examine%20our%20existing%20communication%20channels%20and%20processes.%20We%20audited%20time%20spent%20in%20meetings%2C%20and%20looked%20at%20platforms%20we%20could%20use%20to%20streamline%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20provided%20us%20with%20more%20opportunities%20to%20stay%20heads-down%20in%20the%20work%20or%20step%20away%20and%20gain%20some%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20knew%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20would%20only%20succeed%20if%20it%20benefited%20our%20clients%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20adamant%20that%20we%20would%20only%20move%20forward%20if%20we%20got%20100%25%20client%20buy-in.%20We%20didn't%20receive%20much%20pushback%20from%20clients%20when%20we%20first%20rolled%20out%20the%20four-day%20workweek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20they%20were%20not%20only%20open%20to%20the%20idea%2C%20but%20really%20embraced%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20all%20on%20board%20with%20the%20change%2C%20as%20long%20as%20we%20continued%20to%20get%20the%20work%20done%20and%20meet%20the%20deadlines%20and%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20four-day%20workweek%20hasn't%20had%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20our%20business%20revenue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it's%20been%20quite%20the%20opposite%3A%20RocketAir%20had%20double-digit%20revenue%20growth%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20extended%20weekend%2C%20people%20have%20time%20to%20fully%20recharge%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20new%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-day%20workweek%20also%20gives%20more%20opportunities%20for%20team%20members%20to%20connect%20with%20whatever%20drives%20them%2C%20whether%20it's%20playing%20chess%2C%20visiting%20museums%2C%20taking%20a%20field%20trip%2C%20or%20taking%20an%20improv%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20the%20extra%20time%20for%20hobbies%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20an%20avid%20chess%20player%20and%20play%2020-30%20games%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we're%20approaching%20one%20year%20since%20our%20pilot%20kicked%20off%2C%20truly%20turning%20off%20has%20become%20second%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20try%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20at%20your%20company%2C%20here's%20my%20advice%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20jump%20in%20feet%20first%20without%20a%20preliminary%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Run%20a%20pilot%20for%20at%20least%20three%20months%20to%20experiment%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20optimize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThink%20of%20your%20clients%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20If%20you're%20a%20services%20business%2C%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20will%20succeed%20only%20if%20it%20benefits%20clients%20too.%20Move%20forward%20when%20you%20have%20buy-in%20from%20all%20of%20your%20existing%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDevelop%20a%20thorough%20communications%20strategy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20thought%20through%20every%20possible%20question%20that%20might%20arise%20and%20developed%20messaging%20to%20help%20guide%20internal%20and%20external%20conversations.%20Don't%20just%20announce%20your%20four-day%20workweek%20to%20clients%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20Invite%20them%20into%20the%20conversation%20so%20you%20can%20take%20their%20feedback%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20might%20need%20to%20reconsider%20your%20billing%20model.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20your%20company's%20compensation%20is%20tied%20to%20time%2C%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20will%20be%20less%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20cut%20corners.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20shorter%20workweek%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20pay%20cut%20or%20longer%20days%20is%20not%20a%20sustainable%20solution.%20The%20work%20schedule%20must%20work%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20parents%20and%20caregivers%20on%20your%20team%20who%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20take%20on%20extra%20hours%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModel%20ideal%20behaviors%20for%20your%20team.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20leaders%20and%20people%20managers%20repeatedly%20use%20the%20extra%20day%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20work%2C%20it%20undermines%20the%20culture%20you're%20working%20hard%20to%20create.%20We%20have%20intentional%20conversations%20with%20our%20leadership%20team%20about%20how%20we're%20spending%20our%20day%20off%20and%20hold%20each%20other%20accountable%20to%20unplugging%20on%20Fridays.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20your%20company%20has%20transitioned%20to%20or%20tried%20out%20a%20four-day%20workweek%2C%20email%20Jenna%20Gyimesi%20at%20jgyimesi%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-rocketair-never-going-back-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691745421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d53ef9005c4a00183d81c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-rocketair-never-going-back-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20year%20after%20piloting%20a%204-day%20workweek%2C%20Taylor%20Rosenbauer%20says%20that%20turning%20off%20work%20has%20now%20become%20second%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Robin%20Madell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-day-workweek-rocketair-never-going-back-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Has%20Been%20Without%20Internet%20Services%20for%20100%20Days%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095437%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.01.44-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAugust%2011%20marks%20100%20days%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20100%20days%20since%20the%20state%20government%20first%20shut%20down%20the%20internet.%20The%20high%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpartial%20restoration%E2%80%9D%20of%20internet%20services%20%E2%80%93%20but%2C%20as%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20that%20partial%20restoration%20meets%20the%20needs%20only%20of%20a%20very%20small%20proportion%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20ongoing%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20citizens%20of%20Manipur%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20their%20basic%20human%20rights%E2%80%9D.%20The%20research%20and%20advocacy%20organisation%20has%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20shutdown%20is%20in%20fact%20breeding%20misinformation%2C%20and%20people%20are%20being%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20what%20they%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E100%20Days.%20Today%2C%20August%2011%2C%202023%2C%20marks%20100%20days%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20descent%20into%20a%20state-wide%20internet%20shutdown.%20We%2C%20at%20IFF%2C%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20perturbed%20by%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20and%20how%20the%20citizens%20of%20Manipur%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20their%20basic%20human%20rights.%20It%20contributes%20to%20the%20propagation%20of%20misinformation%20without%20any%20means%20for%20verification%20and%20hinders%20the%20accountability%20process%20for%20human%20rights%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20internet%20access%2C%20which%20was%20imposed%20on%20May%203%2C%202023%2C%20was%20narrowly%20lifted%20on%20July%2025%2C%202023%2C%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20broadband%20services%20(internet%20leased%20line%20and%20fibre%20to%20the%20home)%2C%20even%20though%20broadband%20constitutes%20just%203%25%20of%20all%20internet%20connections%20in%20India.%20What%20is%20quite%20alarming%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20end%20date%20in%20the%20July%2025%20order%20which%20effectively%20makes%20the%20suspension%20indefinite%20in%20nature.%20This%20makes%20the%20order%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eillegal%20as%20it%20violates%20Rule%202(2A)%20of%20the%20Telecom%20Suspension%2C%202017%2C%20as%20amended%20in%202020%2C%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20that%20any%20restrictions%20on%20internet%20services%20must%20be%20temporally%20and%20geographically%20limited.%20Rule%202(2A)%20states%20that%20no%20internet%20suspension%20order%20shall%20be%20in%20operation%20for%20more%20than%20fifteen%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20this%20partial%20restoration%20of%20internet%20services%20comes%20attached%20with%20several%20conditions%2C%20and%20mobile%20data%20services%20remain%20suspended.%20ISPs%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20ensure%20the%20continued%20blocking%20of%20social%20media%20websites%20and%20VPNs%20at%20the%20local%20level%20even%20for%20broadband%20users.%20Physical%20monitoring%20for%20checking%20violation%20of%20terms%20and%20conditions%20may%20also%20be%20undertaken%20by%20the%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20Manipur%20remain%20without%20any%20access%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20such%20disproportionate%20terms%20and%20conditions%20cannot%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20least%20restrictive%20measure%20as%20per%20the%20doctrine%20of%20proportionality%20propounded%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Access%20to%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20banking%20facilities%2C%20and%20livelihood%2C%20are%20all%20impacted.%20The%20economy%20also%20suffers%20drastically.%20Access%20to%20government%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20which%20are%20dependent%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20is%20also%20impeded.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20joint%20report%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20IFF%20on%20the%20human%20impact%20of%20internet%20shutdowns%20documented%20how%20workers%20dependent%20on%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20schemes%2C%20lost%20wages%20as%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20mark%20their%20attendance%20on%20a%20government%20app%20due%20to%20internet%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20procedural%20safeguard%20afforded%20by%20the%20Telecom%20Suspension%20Rules%20against%20internet%20shutdowns%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Review%20Committee%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20which%20must%20meet%20and%20determine%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20orders.%20Disappointingly%2C%20there%20is%20no%20record%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Review%20Committee%20ever%20meeting%20or%20considering%20even%20one%20of%20the%20several%20subsequent%20internet%20shutdown%20orders%20that%20have%20been%20routinely%20passed%20by%20the%20Home%20Department%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20a%20bone-chilling%20video%20has%20emerged%20from%20Manipur%20that%20has%20shattered%20the%20apathy%20and%20silence%20surrounding%20the%20longest%20internet%20shutdown%20in%20the%20country%20in%202023.%20Action%20was%20taken%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20involved%20only%20after%20the%20video%20generated%20explosive%20anger%20across%20the%20public.%20This%20information%20blackhole%20caused%20by%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20has%20not%20only%20had%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20individuals%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20access%20information%20and%20communicate%20freely%2C%20but%20has%20also%20obstructed%20people%20outside%20Manipur%20from%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20ground%20realities%20and%20violence%20that%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20consequent%20information%20disorder%20and%20absence%20of%20internet%20access%20also%20throttles%20voices%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20and%20takes%20away%20their%20ability%20to%20document%20the%20violations%20they%20have%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20egregious%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20shocking%20contempt%20for%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0are%20concerning.%20It%20reveals%20a%20pattern%20of%20paternalistic%20governance%20transpiring%20in%20the%20country%20while%20attempting%20to%20obscure%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%20in%20preventing%20law%20and%20order%20problems.%20In%20such%20dark%20times%2C%20IFF%20expresses%20its%20unwavering%20support%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20reaffirms%20its%20dedication%20to%20championing%20the%20defence%20of%20digital%20rights%20as%20well%20the%20ethical%20utilisation%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691745319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095437%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.01.44-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-has-been-without-internet-services-for-100-days-now%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shutdown%20%26quot%3Bcontributes%20to%20the%20propagation%20of%20misinformation%20without%20any%20means%20for%20verification%20and%20hinders%20the%20accountability%20process%20for%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fth