News%20Of%20His%20Suicide%20On%20Way%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECoaching%20hub%20Kota%20has%20seen%20the%20third%20student%20suicide%20in%20a%20week%2C%20with%20a%2017-year-old%20preparing%20for%20IIT%20JEE%20allegedly%20hanging%20himself%20from%20a%20fan%20in%20his%20hostel%20room.%20Manish%20Prajapati's%20father%20was%20heading%20home%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20after%20meeting%20his%20son%20when%20he%20got%20the%20news%20of%20his%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%2019th%20student%20suicide%20in%20Kota%2C%20which%20is%20also%20known%20as%20'Coaching%20City'%2C%20this%20year.%20Lakhs%20of%20students%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20flock%20to%20the%20education%20hub%20every%20year%20to%20prepare%20for%20competitive%20exams%20and%20gain%20entry%20into%20India's%20top%20engineering%20and%20medical%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Azamgarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20had%20come%20to%20Kota%20four%20months%20ago.%20Police%20said%20he%20was%20not%20doing%20very%20well%20in%20his%20studies%20and%20his%20father%20had%20arrived%20to%20meet%20him%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20had%20left%20Manish's%20hostel%20in%20Mahavir%20Nagar%20to%20return%20home%20last%20evening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish's%20father%20had%20tried%20his%20phone%20around%208%20pm%20and%20then%20called%20on%20the%20number%20for%20the%20hostel%20when%20he%20did%20not%20answer.%20The%20caretaker%2C%20Rakesh%2C%20said%20he%20went%20to%20Manish's%20room%20on%20the%20fifth%20floor%20and%20knocked%20on%20his%20door%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20reply.%20He%20then%20looked%20through%20the%20window%20and%20saw%20Manish%20hanging%20from%20the%20fan%2C%20using%20a%20bedsheet%20as%20a%20noose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20informed%20the%20Jawahar%20Nagar%20police%20station.%20%26quot%3BWe%20informed%20his%20father%2C%20who%20was%20on%20the%20way%20home%20to%20Azamgarh%20and%20is%20now%20coming%20back.%20The%20post-mortem%20of%20the%20dead%20body%20will