89184%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffather-goes-to-kota-to-meet-son-gets-news-of-his-suicide-on-way-back-4289184%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ChatGPT%20and%20GPT-4%20skew%20the%20most%20liberal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Meta's%20LLaMA%20is%20the%20most%20conservative%20AI%20model%2C%20a%20new%20study%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Illustration%20demonstrating%20AI%20bias%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62e40a434b455800188b5e93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20testing%2014%20major%20language%20models%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20GPT-4%20were%20the%20most%20left-leaning%20and%20libertarian%2C%20and%20Meta's%20LLaMA%20AI%20model%20was%20the%20most%20right-leaning%20and%20authoritarian.%3Cp%3ESavanna%20Durr%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt's%20widely%20known%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-discrimination-bias-worse-problem-than-sentience-2022-6%5C%22%3EAI%20has%20a%20bias%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20models%20criticized%20for%20racism%2C%20sexism%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20new%20study%2C%20researchers%20gave%2014%20AI%20models%20a%20political%20compass%20test%20and%20graphed%20the%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20GPT-4%20were%20the%20most%20liberal%2C%20Meta's%20LLaMA%20was%20the%20most%20conservative%2C%20and%20Google's%20BERT%20models%20were%20in%20between.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20widely%20known%20that%20AI%20models%20can%20have%20a%20bias%20problem.%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchatgpt-is-like-many-other-ai-models-rife-with-bias-2023-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChatGPT%252C%2520the%2520latest%2520language%2520learning%2Cspell%2520trouble%2520for%2520marginalized%2520groups.%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-engineer-blake-lemoine-ai-ethics-lamda-racist-2022-7%5C%22%3ELaMDA%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20model%2C%20and%20other%20chatbots%20have%20been%20criticized%20for%20sometimes%20giving%20racist%2C%20sexist%2C%20and%20otherwise%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchatgpt-is-like-many-other-ai-models-rife-with-bias-2023-1%5C%22%3Ebiased%20responses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20say%20they're%20working%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faclanthology.org%2F2023.acl-long.656.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteam%20of%20researchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Washington%2C%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20and%20Xi'an%20Jiaotong%20University%20have%20set%20out%20to%20measure%20political%20biases%20among%20different%20major%20AI%20language%20models%20in%20a%20quantifiable%20way.%20They%20subjected%20each%20model%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politicalcompass.org%2Ftest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolitical%20compass%20test%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20analyzing%20the%20model's%20responses%20to%2062%20different%20political%20statements%20ranging%20from%20%26quot%3Ball%20authority%20should%20be%20questioned%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bmothers%20may%20have%20careers%2C%20but%20their%20first%20duty%20is%20to%20be%20homemakers.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20then%20used%20each%20model's%20responses%20to%20these%20statements%20to%20plot%20all%20the%20language%20models%20on%20a%20political%20compass%20graph%2C%20which%20goes%20from%20left-%20to%20right-leaning%20on%20one%20axis%20and%20libertarian%20to%20authoritarian%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20political%20compass%20test%20as%20a%20metric%20is%20%26quot%3Bfar%20from%20perfect%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20study%20notes%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%20of%20the%2014%20major%20language%20models%20tested%2C%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20GPT-4%20were%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-predict-political-views-liberal-conservative-based-on-looks-study-2023-6%5C%22%3Eleft-leaning%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20libertarian.%20Google's%20BERT%20models%20were%20more%20socially%20conservative%20than%20OpenAI's%20models%2C%20and%20Meta's%20LLaMA%20was%20the%20most%20right-leaning%20and%20authoritarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221516%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20political%20compass%20graph%20from%20the%20study%20that%20shows%20how%20each%20AI%20model%20is%20biased.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d2a8a87d2e90001946b231%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20political%20compass%20graph%20from%20the%20study%20shows%20how%20each%20AI%20model%20is%20biased.%3Cp%3EShangbin%20Feng%2C%20Chan%20Young%20Park%2C%20Yuhan%20Liu%2C%20Yulia%20Tsvetkov%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20looked%20to%20see%20if%20and%20how%20the%20information%20these%20language%20models%20are%20trained%20on%20influences%20their%20political%20biases%20by%20feeding%20two%20models%20%E2%80%94%20OpenAI's%20GPT-2%20(left-leaning%20and%20libertarian)%20and%20Meta's%20RoBERTa%20(center-right%20and%20authoritarian)%20%E2%80%94%20data%20sets%20made%20from%20news%20and%20social%20media%20data%20from%20both%20right%20and%20left-leaning%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20indicated%20that%20this%20process%20further%20reinforced%20the%20models'%20existing%20biases%3A%20the%20left-learning%20model%20became%20more%20left-leaning%2C%20and%20the%20right-leaning%20one%20became%20more%20right-leaning.%20The%20researchers%20also%20found%20that%20political%20biases%20of%20the%20AI%20models%20affected%20how%20the%20models%20responded%20to%20hate%20speech%20and%20what%20they%20identified%20as%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20specific%20comment%20on%20the%20study%2C%20but%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fblog%2Fhow-should-ai-systems-behave%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20company's%20blog%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20AI%20systems%20should%20behave%20and%20a%20snapshot%20of%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.openai.com%2Fsnapshot-of-chatgpt-model-behavior-guidelines.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20model%20behavior%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20robustly%20addressing%20this%20issue%20and%20being%20transparent%20about%20both%20our%20intentions%20and%20our%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20blog%20reads.%20%26quot%3BOur%20guidelines%20are%20explicit%20that%20reviewers%20should%20not%20favor%20any%20political%20group.%20Biases%20that%20nevertheless%20may%20emerge%20from%20the%20process%20described%20above%20are%20bugs%2C%20not%20features.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20representative%20also%20did%20not%20comment%20specifically%20on%20the%20research%2C%20and%20also%20pointed%20to%20a%20Google%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fai.google%2Fresponsibility%2Fresponsible-ai-practices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20responsible%20AI%20practices.%20Part%20of%20the%20post%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20increases%20across%20sectors%20and%20societies%2C%20it%20is%20critical%20to%20work%20towards%20systems%20that%20are%20fair%20and%20inclusive%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20community%20to%20identify%20and%20mitigate%20vulnerabilities%20in%20a%20transparent%20manner%20and%20support%20the%20development%20of%20