20another%20English-speaking%20country%20would%20be%20a%20breeze.%20But%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20the%20differences%20have%20been%20just%20as%20hard%20to%20navigate%20as%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Tokyo.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20culture%20shocks%20I've%20encountered%20and%20how%20I%20survived%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20walking%20down%20the%20street%20in%20New%20York%20city%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d4f80d4dd2b50019c2ce5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrooke%20walking%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emma%20Brooke%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Paris%20and%20Berlin%2C%20I%20met%20Americans%20who%20were%20not-so-pleasantly%20surprised%20at%20their%20European%20salaries.%20But%20soon%20after%20discovering%20that%20a%20coffee%20cost%201%20euro%2C%20they%20learned%20that%20what%20seemed%20like%20a%20little%20went%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20was%20the%20opposite.%20After%20seeing%20my%20paycheck%20almost%20double%20overnight%2C%20I%20started%20imagining%20Fifth%20Avenue%20shopping%20sprees%20and%20a%20roomy%20Manhattan%20apartment.%20But%20my%20first%20month%20stateside%20gave%20me%20a%20reality%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEye-watering%20rents%2C%20huge%20grocery%20bills%2C%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20healthcare%20soon%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20there's%20a%20reason%20the%20salaries%20seemed%20so%20high%3A%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20was%2C%20too.%20My%20monthly%20rent%20of%201%2C000%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%241%2C100%2C%20felt%20like%20a%20lot%20in%20Berlin%20%E2%80%94%20until%20I%20signed%20a%20%243%2C000%20lease%20in%20Brooklyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20move%20to%20the%20US%2C%20do%20your%20research.%20Use%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3