mprising%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%20heard%20several%20petitions%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20were%20two%20women%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20who%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-5-policemen-suspended-over-viral-video-of-sexual-assault%5C%22%3Eparaded%20naked%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob.%20The%20court%20has%20earlier%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20governments%E2%80%99%20handling%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20over%20three%20months%2C%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20150%20people%20and%20to%20tens%20of%20thousands%20being%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-police%5C%22%3Eit%20had%20called%20police%20investigation%20%E2%80%9Ctardy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asked%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20to%20be%20present%20in%20court%20to%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20judges.%20In%20its%20August%207%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20has%20repeated%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Ctardy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20a%20considerable%20lapse%20between%20the%20occurrence%20and%20the%20registration%20of%20FIRs%2C%20recording%20of%20witness%20statements%20and%20even%20the%20arrests%20are%20few%20and%20far%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupervision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20August%207%20order%2C%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20process%20of%20investigation%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20shall%20be%20monitored%20by%20the%20apex%20court.%20Former%20Maharashtra%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Dattatray%20Padsalgikar%2C%20was%20appointed%20supervisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20directed%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20to%20place%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20CBI%2C%20five%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police-rank%20officers%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%20and%20the%20Delhi%20National%20Capital%20Territory%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20a%20woman.%20These%20officers%20will%20need%20to%20submit%20periodical%20information%20and%20reports%20to%20Padsalgikar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20asked%20Padsalgikar%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20that%20certain%20police%20officers%20colluded%20with%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20(including%20sexual%20violence)%20during%20the%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20and%20submit%20a%20report%20to%20the%20court.%20It%20directed%20the%20Union%20and%20Manipur%20governments%20to%20provide%20any%20assistance%20required%20in%20order%20to%20carry%20out%20this%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ordered%20the%20formation%20of%20no%20fewer%20than%2042%20special%20investigation%20teams.%20One%2C%20headed%20by%20a%20superintendent-rank%20officer%20to%20look%20at%20FIRs%20related%20to%20murder%20and%20other%20heinous%20crimes%2C%20and%20another%2C%20including%20a%20female%20inspector%20for%20FIRs%20related%20to%20rape%2C%20outraging%20of%20modesty%20and%20such%20other%20sexual%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20FIRs%20will%20be%20investigated%20by%20SITs%20headed%20by%20an%20officer%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20for%20six%20SITs%20for%20the%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20Bishnupur%20and%20Kakching%2C%20and%20three%20for%20Thoubal%20and%20Tengnoupal%20districts.%20These%20SITs%20will%20be%20supervised%20weekly%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%2C%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%20or%20additional%20director%20general.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20DGP%20will%20also%20monitor%20these%20cases%20fortnightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20also%20said%20that%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20proper%20monitoring%20and%20supervision%20of%20the%20investigation%20by%20the%20police%20authorities%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20shall%20depute%20one%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20Police%20Inspector%20each%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi.%20At%20least%2014%20officers%20not%20below%20the%20rank%20of%20superintendent%20of%20police%20are%20to%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20respective%20SITs%2C%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESITs%20comprising%20women%20officers%20should%20be%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20investigation%20of%20crimes%20involving%20sexual%20violence.%20The%20court%20also%20mandated%20that%20SITs%20probing%20such%20violence%20stick%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20directions%20issued%20in%20%3Cem%3ENipun%20Saxena%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20XYZ%20v.%20State%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwe-cant-justify-what-happened-in-manipur-by-saying-this-happened-elsewhere-sc%5C%22%3Eon%20July%2031%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20sexual%20violence%20incident%20in%20Manipur%20cannot%20be%20justified%20by%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20and%20this%20happened%20elsewhere%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStress%20on%20inclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20in%20its%20August%207%20order%20also%20said%20that%20each%20SIT%20will%20visit%20each%20relief%20camp%20within%20the%20area%20assigned%20to%20it%20and%20make%20it%20known%20that%20it%20is%20an%20impartial%20body%20which%20is%20accepting%20complaints%20of%20violence%2C%20including%20sexual%20violence.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20necessary%20because%20many%20survivors%20%2F%20victims%20may%20not%20approach%20the%20police%20machinery%20of%20their%20own%20accord%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20sectarian%20violence%20which%20may%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20family%20members%20and%20homes%2C%20displacement%2C%20and%20trauma%20to%20their%20own%20bodies%20and%20minds%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20also%20said%20that%20SITs%20constituted%20by%20Manipur%20government%20shall%20not%20consist%20exclusively%20of%20members%20belonging%20to%20either%20one%20of%20the%20communities%20involved%20in%20the%20clashes%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20victims%20of%20violence%20must%20receive%20remedial%20measures%20irrespective%20of%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20it%20said%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20irrespective%20of%20the%20source%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20addressed%20widespread%20concerns%20over%20police%20having%20favoured%20one%20community%20over%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20serious%20allegations%20including%20witness%20statements%20indicating%20that%20the%20law-enforcing%20machinery%20has%20been%20inept%20in%20controlling%20the%20violence%20and%2C%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20colluded%20with%20the%20perpetrators.%20Absent%20a%20proper%20investigation%2C%20this%20Court%20will%20not%20enter%20a%20finding%20of%20fact%20on%20these%20allegations.%20But%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20such%20allegations%20require%20an%20objective%20fact-finding%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20a%20breach%20of%20public%20duty%20must%20equally%20be%20brought%20to%20account%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20rank%2C%20position%2C%20or%20post%2C%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20officer%20of%20the%20state%20or%20other%20employee%20of%20the%20state%20who%20is%20guilty%20no