0Bill%2C%202023%20--%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20panel%20for%20further%20scrutiny%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20changed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20announced%20that%20the%20sedition%20law%20has%20been%20repealed.%20The%20word%20%26quot%3Bsedition%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20proposed%20law%20and%20replaced%20with%20Section%20150%2C%20which%20criminalises%20acts%20that%20endanger%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20law%20on%20sedition%20carries%20a%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20three%20years%20in%20prison%20or%20life%20imprisonment.%20The%20new%20provision%20increases%20the%20maximum%20penalty%20to%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20announced%20in%20the%20parliament%20that%20the%20government%20will%20introduce%20the%20death%20penalty%20for%20mob%20lynching%20cases%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20crime.%20The%20death%20sentence%20has%20been%20retained%20in%20the%20new%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20bills%20prioritise%20laws%20that%20protect%20women%20and%20children%2C%20punish%20murderers%2C%20and%20deter%20those%20who%20would%20harm%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20proposed%20laws%2C%20bribing%20voters%20during%20elections%20is%20a%20punishable%20offense%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunity%20service%20is%20a%20new%20non-custodial%20punishment%20that%20will%20be%20available%20for%20petty%20offenses%20in%20India%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20laws%20have%20also%20made%20offences%20gender-neutral%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20that%20everyone%20is%20protected%20from%20crime%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20gender.%20In%20order%20to%20deal%20effectively%20with%20terrorism%20and%20organised%20crime%2C%20new%20offences%20have%20been%20created%20with%20severe%20penalties.%