2C%20under%20the%20Swadesh%20Darshan%20Scheme.%20Irregularities%20include%20undue%20benefits%20to%20contractors%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcag-undue-benefits-to-contractors-in-ayodhya-development-project-8886869%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20audited%20the%20Swadesh%20Darshan%20Scheme%20between%20January%202015%20to%20March%202022.%20The%20report%20from%20the%20audit%20was%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20stated%20that%20undue%20benefits%20of%20Rs%2019.73%20crore%20were%20made%20to%20contractors%20in%20six%20projects%2Fcircuits%20across%20six%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20undue%20benefits%20specific%20to%20the%20Ayodhya%20project%2C%20the%20CAG%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20contractor%20engaged%20by%20the%20implementing%20agency%20viz.%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Rajkiya%20Nirman%20Nigam%2C%20was%20required%20to%20submit%20performance%20guarantee%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20five%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20contract%20price%20of%20Rs%2062.17%20crore%2C%20which%20worked%20out%20to%20Rs%203.11%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20contractor%20submitted%20a%20lesser%20amount%20of%20performance%20guarantee%20i.e.%2C%20Rs%201.86%20crore%20only%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20renewal%20(September%202021)%20without%20citing%20any%20reason%20on%20record.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWork%20at%20Guptar%20Ghat%2C%20Ayodhya%20was%20split%20into%2014%20lots%20of%20equal%20sizes%20and%20works%20were%20awarded%20to%20different%20private%20contractors.%20However%2C%20the%20executing%20agency%20(Irrigation%20Department)%20did%20not%20take%20due%20care%20in%20making%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20the%20financial%20bids%2Frates%20offered%20by%20the%20contractors%20and%20awarded%20works%20of%20similar%20nature%20and%20sanctioned%20costs%20to%20the%20same%20contractors%20but%20at%20varying%20rates%20resulting%20in%20failure%20to%20save%20Rs%2019.13%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGST%20registrations%20of%20three%20contractors%20were%20cancelled%20by%20the%20state%20government%20suo%20motu%20after%20awarding%20of%20works%20to%20them.%20Thus%2C%20they%20were%20no%20more%20registered%20contractors%20and%20were%20not%20entitled%20to%20collect%20GST.%20However%2C%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2019.57%20lakh%20was%20irregularly%20paid%20to%20one%20contractor%20against%20his%20GST%20registration%20and%20in%20case%20of%20other%20two%20contractors%2C%20it%20was%20pending%20for%20payment%2C%20whereas%20full%20amount%20of%20GST%20was%20liable%20to%20be%20deducted%20and%20deposited%20by%20the%20executing%20agency%20(Irrigation%20Department)%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20the%20CAG%20report%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContractors%20were%20paid%20for%20work%20that%20has%20not%20been%20executed%2C%20the%20CAG%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20of%20development%20of%20the%20Guptar%20Ghat%20included%20work%20of%2023%2C767%20sq.mtr%20%E2%80%98supplying%20and%20fixing%20of%20stone%20patia%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%201%2C447.50%20per%20sq.mtr.%20This%20work%20included%20the%20cost%20of%20MS%20clamp%20(supply%20and%20fixing)%20at%20Rs%20216.88%20per%20sq.mtr.%20(Rs%20136.88%20for%20supply%20and%20Rs%2080.00%20for%20fixing).%20The%20work%20was%20executed%20and%20payment%20was%20made%20to%20the%20private%20contractors%20at%20the%20rates%20quoted%20by%20them%20in%20their%20respective%20agreements%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20five%20projects%20mentioned%20in%20the%20report%20are%20the%20development%20of%20Sinquerim-Aguada%20Jail%2C%C2%A0Goa%3B%20Himalayan%20Circuit%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%3B%20Heritage%20Circuit%2C%20Telangana%3B%20development%20of%20Rangpo-Singtam%2C%20Sikkim%3B%20and%20Buddhist%20Circuit%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691740858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F29154416%2F1280px-Ayodhya_100_34.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-finds-irregularities-in-ayodhya-development-project%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20says%20undue%20benefits%20were%20given%20to%20contractors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-report-finds-irregularities-in-ayodhya-development-project%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Provisions%20for%20sedition%20offences%20to%20be%20completely%20repealed%2C%20says%20Amit%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691740601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F09%2Ffull%2F1691583494-7981.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fprovisions-for-sedition-offences-to-be-completely-repealed-says-amit-shah-123081100296_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shah%20also%20said%20that%20the%20provision%20of%20capital%20punishment%20will%20also%20be%20introduced%20in%20mob%20lynching%20cases%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fprovisions-for-sedition-offences-to-be-completely-repealed-says-amit-shah-123081100296_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fprovisions-for-sedition-offences-to-be-completely-repealed-says-amit-shah-123081100296_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fprovisions-for-sedition-offences-to-be-completely-repealed-says-amit-shah-123081100296_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20and%20Mewat%3A%20On%20Reading%20Two%20Landscapes%20of%20Social%20Suffering%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09192254%2Fimage-1205.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20of%20this%20beautiful%20land%20is%20widespread%20and%20seemingly%20unending.%20It%20touches%20us%20closely.%20Two%20members%20of%20our%20family%20are%20from%20Imphal%20and%20my%20niece%20is%20named%20after%20its%20river%2C%20Iril.%20In%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20I%20travelled%20several%20times%20through%20the%20state%2C%20always%20surprised%20at%20the%20levels%20of%20under%20development.%20Imphal%20did%20not%20even%20have%20a%20decent%20cafe%20or%20a%20book%20shop.%20As%20a%20historian-anthropologist%20of%20Mewat%2C%20I%20have%20also%20travelled%20in%20the%20villages%20and%20towns%20inhabited%20by%20the%20Indian%20Meos%20since%201985%20and%20seen%20closely%20the%20backwardness%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20seven%20states%20of%20the%20northeast%2C%20a%20corrupt%20elite%20has%20constantly%20been%20siphoning%20off%20Central%20funds.%20Development%20continues%20to%20mean%20largely%20%E2%80%9Cinfrastructure.%E2%80%9D%20In%20Mewat%2C%20likewise%2C%20a%20Mewat%20Development%20Agency%2FBoard%20was%20set%20up%20but%20during%20my%20fieldwork%20I%20heard%20numerous%20complaints%20that%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20the%20entrenched%20backwardness%20of%20the%20Meo%20community%2C%20its%20funds%20were%20utilised%20largely%20for%20building%20roads%2C%20which%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20the%20task%20of%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(PWD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roots%20of%20the%20problem%20run%20deep.%20Colonialism%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20Mizoram%20simultaneously%20introduced%20writing%2C%20the%20state%20and%20the%20modern%20idea%20of%20religion.%20Ethnology%20sought%20to%20map%20racial%20distinctions%20and%20Christian%20missionaries%20converted%20peoples%20whom%20colonial%20knowledge%20had%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctribals%E2%80%9D%20and%20people%20without%20religion.%20Among%20the%20Nagas%2C%20the%20British%20created%20an%20aspiration%20for%20a%20Greater%20Nagaland%2C%20thinking%20of%20this%20as%20a%20continuing%20foothold%20for%20themselves%20even%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20would%20be%20decolonised.%20The%20latest%20missionaries%20are%20those%20attempting%20to%20spread%20a%20packaged%20Hinduism%2C%20as%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20Missionaries%20also%20appear%20in%20secular%20guise%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Ulfa-Maoist%20alliance%20responsible%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Sanjoy%20Ghose%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20nationalism%20was%20particularly%20strong%20and%20rallied%20around%20the%20figure%20of%20the%20king.%20Its%20backbone%20was%20the%20major%20community%20of%20the%20Meitei%2C%20which%20had%20come%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20Vaishnava%20Hindu%20practice%20and%20created%20a%20culture%20richly%20endowed%20with%20music%20and%20dance%2C%20literature%20and%20theatre.%20It%20is%20supremely%20ironic%20that%20this%20community%20came%20to%20spawn%20a%20large%20number%20of%20terror%20organisations%20in%20postcolonial%20India.%20Why%20this%20came%20to%20be%20so%20is%20a%20question%20that%20should%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20all%20Indians.%20Both%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20Manipur%2C%20the%20footprint%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20was%20the%20largest%20and%20spawned%20the%20spiral%20of%20violence%20and%20counter-violence%20fostered%20also%20by%20the%20supply%20of%20arms%C2%A0%20from%20China%20and%20Burma%20to%20terror%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20closely%20followed%20the%20story%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20protest%20against%20the%20Indian%20army%20and%20read%20during%20a%20long%20stay%20in%20Imphal%20Teresa%20Rehman%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Mothers%20of%20Manipu%3C%2Fem%3Er%3Cem%3E%3A%20The%20Twelve%20Women%20who%20Made%20History%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebased%20on%20her%20moving%20interviews%20of%20how%20women%20responded%20to%20the%20rape%20of%20Manorama%20in%20July%202004.%20At%20a%20tense%20meeting%20held%20in%20a%20closed%20room%20in%20the%20Ima%20Keithel%20women%E2%80%99s%20market%2C%20a%20dozen%20women%20agreed%20to%20strip%20naked%20and%20hold%20up%20a%20banner%20with%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Army%20rape%20us%E2%80%99.%20The%20protest%20was%20kept%20absolutely%20secret%20even%20from%20their%20husbands%20and%20families%20and%20some%20even%20fainted%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20protest%20held%20outside%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20Kangla%20Fort.%20The%20Army%20commander%20eventually%20came%20out%20and%20bowed%20before%20the%20women.%20On%20November%2020%2C%202004%2C%20the%20fort%20%E2%80%93%20a%20symbol%20of%20Manipuri%20nationalism%20%E2%80%93%20was%20handed%20back%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%20King%20Khagemba%20(1597-1652)%20had%20built%20this%20fort%20where%20the%20universe%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20centred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20digest%20that%20in%202023%20women%20used%20themselves%20as%20human%20shields%20in%20the%20pitched%20battles%20between%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20gangs.%20There%20are%20many%20factors%20that%20have%20created%20this%20round%20of%20violence.%20The%20Meitei%20demand%20is%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20that%20seeks%20for%20the%20community%20the%20benefits%20of%20affirmative%20action%20and%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20hill%20areas.%20Currently%2C%20Kukis%20can%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20valley%20but%20the%20Meitei%20do%20not%20have%20the%20reciprocal%20right%20and%20feel%20that%20the%20valley%20is%20getting%20crowded.%20The%20land%20in%20the%20hills%20is%20mineral%20rich.%20Finally%2C%20there%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-poppy-national-security-golden-triangle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erole%20of%20the%20drug%20lords%20in%20collaboration%20with%20actors%20at%20various%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20the%20larger%20region%20known%20as%20the%20Golden%20Triangle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20Nuh%20conflict%20likewise%20has%20two%20centuries%20of%20colonial%20rule%20behind%20it%2C%20particularly%20the%20play%20of%20the%20categories%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20colonise%20contemporary%20India.%20In%20the%20census%20you%20could%20be%20either%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim%2C%20not%20both%20simultaneously%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20the%20closest%20approximation%20to%20Meo%20practice%2C%20as%20indeed%2C%20they%20venerated%20both%20Sufi%20saints%20and%20Shiva%2FMahadeva.%20Over%20a%20period%2C%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20Mewatis%E2%80%9D%20shrunk%20and%20then%20disappeared%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENuh%2C%20Taoru%2C%20Nagina%2C%20Punhana%20and%20Ferozepur%20Jhirka%2C%20the%20five%20blocks%20of%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20district%20of%20Nuh%20(created%20in%202013)%20have%20been%20among%20the%20poorest%20areas%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Punjab.%20These%20were%20the%20drylands%20of%20low%20productivity%20exacerbated%20by%20cycles%20of%20famine%20and%20stringent%20colonial%20revenue%20collection.%20Little%20wonder%20that%20anti-colonial%20feeling%20was%20particularly%20high%20among%20the%20Meos.%20Insurgency%20affected%20both%20the%20Rajasthan%20and%20Punjab%20areas%20of%20Mewat%20in%201857%20and%20the%20British%20made%20the%20Meos%20pay%20for%20it.%20Subsequent%20state%20investment%20in%20canals%20was%20largely%20in%20areas%20inhabited%20by%20the%20Jats%2C%20seen%20as%20the%20stolid%20Victorian%20peasants%2C%20but%20rendered%20both%20Meo%20and%20Gujjar%20villages%20significantly%20impoverished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20reports%20highlight%20the%20high%20fertility%20rate%20of%20the%20Meos%20of%20Nuh%20and%20also%20their%20backwardness%20in%20terms%20of%20female%20literacy%20but%20ignore%20the%20other%20components%20of%20backwardness%20such%20as%20the%20declining%20political%20representation%20of%20the%20Meos%20compared%20with%20other%20backward%20caste%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Jats%20and%20Yadavs.%20This%20was%20a%20result%20partly%20of%20the%20partition%20exodus%20of%20the%20Meos%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20genocidal%20violence%20of%20the%20princely%20states%20of%20Alwar%20and%20Bharatpur%20in%20alliance%20with%20a%20new%20social%20formation%2C%20a%20notorious%20intercaste%20coalition%20called%20AJGAR%2C%20its%20constituents%20being%20Ahirs%2C%20Jats%20and%20Gujars%20who%20had%20for%20centuries%20lived%20peacefully%20with%20the%20Meos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hunger%20for%20land%20was%20tremendous%20among%20these%20peasant%20groups%20and%20what%20better%20excuse%20to%20decimate%20the%20Meos%20and%20cause%20them%20to%20migrate%20than%20the%20Muslim%20League%20movement%20for%20Pakistan.%20It%20did%20not%20matter%20that%20the%20Meo%20leadership%20was%20largely%20pro-Congress%20and%20against%20Jinnah%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20League%20and%20the%20movement%20for%20Pakistan.%20They%20could%20and%20were%20accused%20of%20creating%20a%20Meoistan%20analogous%20to%20Pakistan!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20decades%20before%20Partition%2C%20a%20new%2C%20hyper-nationalist%20popular%20history%20had%20been%20created%20that%20constructed%20the%20Meos%20as%20exclusively%20Muslim.%20This%20new%20history%20is%20postulated%20on%20forgetting%2C%20an%20erasure%20of%20the%20past.%20The%20Meos%20had%20been%20regarded%20by%20the%20British%20as%20half-Hindu%3B%20they%20shared%20in%20the%20practices%20of%20pastoral-agrarian%20culture%20such%20as%20the%20jajmani%20patronage%20of%20dependent%20castes%3B%20a%20kinship%20system%20in%20which%20cross-cousin%20marriage%20(what%20they%20call%20%3Cem%3Ekaka-tau%20mein%20nikah%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20anathema%3B%20the%20seasonal%20cycles%20of%20festivals%20and%20pilgrimages%20to%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20Govardhan%20Yatra%20%E2%80%93%20after%20all%2C%20Krishna%20was%20the%20progenitor%20of%20the%20Meo%20Jadu%20clans%2C%20as%20Rama%20was%20of%20the%20Meo%20Badgujar%20clans%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20the%20Mahadeva%20shrine%20in%20the%20hills%20for%20it%20was%20always%20Shiva%20who%20came%20to%20assist%20them%20at%20moments%20of%20crisis%20and%20in%20their%20struggle%20with%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20history%20of%20the%20Meos%20as%20cow%20killers%20also%20ignores%20the%20massive%20effort%20at%20cow%20protection%20by%20the%20Meo%20panchayats%3B%20that%20many%20Meos%20kept%20cows%20and%20that%20many%20Meo%20women%20would%20craft%20stacks%20of%20cowdung%20cakes%20with%20floral%20designs.%20In%20the%20Mewati%20Mahabharata%20the%20five%20Pandava%20brothers%20graze%20cows%20while%20their%20shared%20wife%2C%20Draupadi%2C%20is%20an%20incarnation%20of%20the%20goddess%2C%20capable%20of%20the%20curse%20of%20great%20destruction%20that%20will%20be%20wrought%20on%20the%20Kaurava%20army%20after%20she%20is%20publicly%20disrobed%20in%20Duryodhana%E2%80%99s%20court!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20Mewat%20has%20been%20whiplashed%20by%20violence%20again%20and%20again.%20The%20most%20recent%20phase%20began%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20has%20been%20fuelled%20by%20the%20VHP%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20Acharya%20Dharmendra%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20of%20the%20Dharma%20Sansad%2C%20once%20told%20me%20that%20Mewat%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccold%E2%80%9D%20area%20(read%3A%20where%20inter-communal%20violence%20has%20been%20relatively%20less).%20Cow%20killing%20became%20the%20cry%20against%20the%20Meos%20as%20the%20VHP%20intensified%20the%20heat%2C%20creating%20crisis%20after%20crisis%20in%20the%20Bharatpur%2C%20Alwar%20districts%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20then%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Mewat%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Nuh%20and%20Gurgaon%2FGurugram%20have%20been%20host%20to%20cow%20vigilante%20groups%20and%20episodes%20of%20lynching%2C%20the%20public%20executions%20carried%20out%20by%20vigilante%20groups%20in%20the%20name%20of%20cow%20protection.%20Asif%20Khan%20of%20Khalilpur%20Kheda%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fasif-khan-lynched-mewat-haryana-police-arrests-accused%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elynched%20by%20a%20mob%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20was%20returning%20from%20buying%20medicine%3B%20Nasir%20and%20Junaid%20were%20allegedly%20attacked%20and%20abducted%20in%20February%202023.%20According%20to%20the%20chargesheet%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20police%2C%20the%20Haryana%20police%20refused%20to%20register%20a%20case%20against%20them%2C%20after%20which%20their%20bodies%20were%20set%20ablaze%20by%20a%20gang%20said%20to%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fjunaid-nasir-murder-chargesheet-rinku-saini-monu-manesar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvolved%20with%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leader%2C%20Mohit%20Yadav%20known%20as%20Monu%20Manesar.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparation%20for%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20violence%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20procession%20devised%20three%20years%20ago%20to%20a%20temple.%20Videos%20were%20circulated%2C%20announcing%20the%20presence%20of%20gangsters%20Monu%20Manesar%20and%20Bijju%20Bajrangi.%20According%20to%20press%20reports%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfI4crZ2ZE_Q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintelligence%20report%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20but%20not%20passed%20on%20to%20the%20home%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20likewise%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20police%20following%20an%20alert%20by%20the%20Nuh%20Peace%20Committee.%20A%20deliberately%20circulated%20rumour%20of%20the%20arrival%20of%20Monu%20Manesar%20in%20a%20vehicle%20led%20to%20stone%20pelting%20by%20Meos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20all%20shops%20and%20businesses%20in%20Gurgaon%20were%20asked%20to%20remove%20Muslims%20from%20the%20premises%20else%20they%20would%20be%20treated%20as%20traitors.%20Within%20days%20Muslims%20including%20cobblers%2C%20tailors%20and%20labour%20fled%20from%20four%20districts%20of%20the%20Haryana%20State.%20The%20only%20exception%20were%20the%20Bengalis%20as%20without%20them%20Gurgaon%E2%80%99s%20services%20would%20collapse.%20The%20bulldozer%20then%20began%20its%20work%2C%20razing%20the%20homes%20of%20Nuh%20residents%C2%A0%20until%20it%20was%20called%20to%20a%20halt%20by%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20defined%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20as%20a%20land%20of%20communities.%20Living%20together%2C%20rural%20and%20urban%20socialites%20have%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20its%20civilisation%20for%20several%20millennia.%20Is%20this%20fabric%20coming%20asunder%20is%20a%20question%20all%20Indians%20must%20ask%20themselves%20today.%20If%20so%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20recognise%20the%20sources%20of%20violence%20through%20deep%20readings%20of%20the%20past%20as%20a%20prelude%20to%20action.%20The%20present%20scenario%20looks%20bleak%20with%20only%20institutions%20such%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20a%20bulwark%20for%20Manipur%20and%20the%20inter-communal%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Movement%20as%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20in%20Mewat%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShail%20Mayaram%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Secret%20Life%20of%20Another%20Indian%20Nationalism%3A%20Transitions%20from%20the%20Pax%20Britannica%20to%20the%20Pax%20Americana%3Cem%3E%2C%20published%20by%20Cambridge%20University%20Press.%20She%20is%20an%20honorary%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20in%20Delhi.%20She%20is%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Academic%20Advisory%20Board%20at%20the%20K%C3%A4te%20Hamburger%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Apocalyptic%20and%20Postapocalyptic%20Studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Heidelberg.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691