.%20Our%20System%20Failed%20It.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20A.K.%20Vishvesha%20allowed%20an%20application%20moved%20by%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masjid%20Committee%2C%20which%20said%20that%20though%20the%20ASI%20has%20not%20issued%20any%20statements%20regarding%20the%20survey%2C%20incorrect%20and%20untrue%20information%20is%20being%20disseminated%20haphazardly%20across%20social%2C%20print%20and%20electronic%20media.%20The%20application%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20been%20publishing%20and%20disseminating%20information%20related%20to%20the%20areas%20inside%20the%20mosque%20which%20have%20not%20been%20surveyed%20to%20date%2C%20due%20to%20which%2C%20there%20is%20a%20wrong%20impact%20on%20the%20daily%20life%20of%20the%20public%20and%20different%20types%20of%20things%20are%20being%20generated%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20public%20and%20the%20enmity%20is%20spreading.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20case%20pertains%20to%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20four%20Hindu%20women%20who%20have%20sought%20access%20to%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20premises%20year%20round%20to%20offer%20prayers%20on%20what%20they%20claim%20was%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20had%20earlier%20allowed%20the%20ASI%20to%20conduct%20its%20survey%2C%20upholding%20a%20lower%20court%20order%2C%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20later%20upheld%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691727951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F15184329%2F20230103_124657.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcourt-tells-asi-stakeholders-not-to-give-media-unofficial-info-on-gyanvapi-mosque-survey%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20A.K.%20Vishvesha%20allowed%20an%20application%20moved%20by%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masjid%20Committee%2C%20which%20said%20that%20though%20the%20ASI%20has%20not%20issued%20an